N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4403.12 - Corporation rules and regulations

State Regulations
A corporation may propose rules and regulations with
respect to the implementation of such corporation's plan of operation. Such
rules and regulations shall not become effective without the prior approval of
the commission. Notes
